<br>
One of the biggest problems I have always had with playing the caster classes (coming from a strict melee background) was no matter how much I tried, I would always get a spell in a different slot when I needed to remem things (thus needing to change around my hotkeys since now X spell is in Y slot instead of Z slot like it should have been).<br>
<br>
Any suggestions on what spells to mem in the eight slots available?  What spells I should keep up?  I know being low level (and a lot of posters here being high level) my spells won't be the same, but any advice is greatly appreciated.<br>
<br>
And along those lines, any suggestions on hot key setups to make use of the 10 buttons available?<br>
<br>
Well, guess to be honest I am not looking for advice as much as what other people do. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Guess I have always learned better by modifying what other people to my own uses...  Thanks for any advice and information that you can give.<br>
<br>
